{"lemma":"فَحْمُ","slug":"فَحْمُ","root":"ف.ح.م","root_slug":"ف-ح-م","root_link":"/words/roots/ف-ح-م","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n33156","n33159","n33160","n33161"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%81%D9%8E%D8%AD%D9%92%D9%85%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"cinder","tags":["collective"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"coal; charcoal","tags":["collective"],"examples":[{"text":"فَحْم حَجَرِيّ","english":"coal (carbon rock)"},{"text":"فَحْم الْخَشَب","english":"charcoal"}]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From the root ف ح م (f ḥ m). Cognate with Hebrew פֶּחָם (peḥām, “coal”), Aramaic ܦܲܚܡܵܐ (paḥmā, “coal”)."},"ipa":["/faħm/","/ˈfɐħəm/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n33156","headword_ar":"فَحُمَ","root":"fHm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fuHuwmN","text_ar":"فُحُومٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fuHuwmapN","text_ar":"فُحُومَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, * TA,) said of anything, (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, black"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faHom","text_ar":"فَحْم"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"charcoal"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (K, TA.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faAHimN","text_ar":"فَاحِمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faHomN","text_ar":"فَحْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", last sentence.       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faHama","text_ar":"فَحَمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Ks, S, Msb, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (Ks, S, Msb, TA,) accord. to the K"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is wrong; (TA;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faHima","text_ar":"فَحِمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fuHima","text_ar":"فُحِمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a boy, or child,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wept until his voice became stopped;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ks, S, Msb;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"until his breath became stopped;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ufoHima","text_ar":"اُفْحِمَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) ―         -b2-  And, said of a ram, (K,) or thus"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faHama","text_ar":"فَحَمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faHima","text_ar":"فَحِمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"manaEa","text_ar":"مَنَعَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ealima","text_ar":"عَلِمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He uttered a cry,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cries."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.) And (TA) one says of a ram,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vagaA Hat~aY faHama","text_ar":"ثَغَا حَتَّى فَحَمَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He bleated until"},{"kind":"page_break","n":2347},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he became hoarse."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faHama","text_ar":"فَحَمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", said of a man,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was unable to answer,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,) when one had spoken to him. (TA.) ―         -b4-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faHamati Alqaliybu","text_ar":"فَحَمَتِ القَلِيبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fuHuwmN","text_ar":"فُحُومٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The well,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"old well,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ceased to have a flow of water."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["K","TA","Ks","S","Msb"]},{"entry_id":"n33159","headword_ar":"فَحْمٌ","root":"fHm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faHamN","text_ar":"فَحَمٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, K,) the latter sometimes occurring, (S, Msb,) like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nahorN","text_ar":"نَهْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naharN","text_ar":"نَهَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Charcoal;"},{"kind":"text","text":"this is what is meant by its being said to signify]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"extinct coal;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a thing well known;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faHiymN","text_ar":"فَحِيمٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, K;) or, accord. to ISd, this may be a pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faHomN","text_ar":"فَحْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [or a quasi-pl. n.,] like as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EabiydN","text_ar":"عَبِيدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EabodN","text_ar":"عَبْدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maEiyzN","text_ar":"مَعِيزٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maEozN","text_ar":"مَعْزٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", &c.: (TA:) the n. un. [meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a piece of charcoal"},{"kind":"text","text":"] is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faHomapN","text_ar":"فَحْمَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K, TA,) but not"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faHamapN","text_ar":"فَحَمَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)       -A2-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faHomN","text_ar":"فَحْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies also The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"draught that is drunk in"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any one of"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the times denoted by the word"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faHomapN","text_ar":"فَحْمَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]: (K, TA:) like the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gabuwq","text_ar":"غَبُوق"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SabuwH","text_ar":"صَبُوح"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaA$iriy~ap","text_ar":"جَاشِرِيَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qayol","text_ar":"قَيْل"},{"kind":"text","text":": but it is disapproved by Az. (TA.) ―         -b2-  [Accord. to the TK, it is an inf. n. of which the verb is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faHama","text_ar":"فَحَمَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", signifying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a man)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"drank in the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faHomap","text_ar":"فَحْمَة"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ei$aA='","text_ar":"عِشَا=ء"},{"kind":"text","text":": but of this I find not any confirmation.]"}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n33160","headword_ar":"فَحَمٌ","root":"fHm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see the next preceding paragraph."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n33161","headword_ar":"فَحِمٌ","root":"fHm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faAHimN","text_ar":"فَاحِمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}